"3. side-load / install the OTA zip file to your phone, the same way you would\n"
"  install a custom ROM. (eg. with `adb`, `heimdall`, etc.)\n"
msgstr ""
"1. загрузите последнюю версию [F-Droid привилегированное расширение OTA](https://f-droid.org/packages/org.fdroid.fdroid.privileged.ota/#suggested).\n"
